## Changes in GoCD 26.1.0

No deprecations.

### Logging

Plugins targeting GoCD 26.1.0+ can now provide a logger name via a string; allowing custom log redirectors to be
written (e.g custom SLF4J implementations which delegate to GoCD's plugin logging API).

```java
import com.thoughtworks.go.plugin.api.logging.Logger;
//...

private static final Logger LOG = Logger.getLoggerFor("my-logger", MyPlugin.PLUGIN_ID);

// Rather than one of:
private static final Logger LOG = Logger.getLoggerFor(MyPlugin.class);
private static final Logger LOG = Logger.getLoggerFor(MyPlugin.class, MyPlugin.PLUGIN_ID);
```
